dc_description_s: The Platts Natural Gas Utility Service Territories geospatial data layer contains regions representing the geographic extent of retail service provided by natural gas utilities in North America.  Included in the attribute information are revenues, rates, # of customers, and total Mcf's delivered for residential, commercial, industrial, and electric utility sales by natural gas utility.
dc_title_s: North America (Natural Gas Utility Service Territories, Dec. 2008)
